metatags.sailthru.excerpt: Since becoming the Duchess of Sussex, Meghan Markle has ushered in a new wave of modernity and minimalism to the British royal family’s style. Known for her monochromatic outfits, boat necklines, and even suits (no pun intended), Meghan has quickly become a style icon across the globe. The royal is known to frequent designers like Givenchy and Dior, while also mixing in more affordable finds from brands like Artizia and J.Crew too. With all eyes on the duchess, we’re tracking all her best outfits and style since she first went public with Prince Harry in 2017.
